snippet.title: Nidhogg 2 Teaser
snippet.description:
The next installment of the epic award-winning dueling tug-of-war is coming! Destroy your opponents with all new moves and weapons across ten different arenas. Enjoy new monstrous visuals by artist Toby Dixon and bangin Beats from Daedelus, Mux Mool, Doseone, and more!  Coming in 2017!!

Game by Messhof www.messhof.com  @messhof @kr15t3a

More info at www.nidhogggame.com

Art by Toby Dixon www.tonydixob.tumblr.com

"Raw Gore"
Performed by Mux Mool  @muxmool
Courtesy of Ghostly International @ghostly @ghostlysongs

Logos by Cory Schmitz @CorySchmitz

Trailer by Matt Chandronait - Area5 www.area5.tv
